  "remarks": "\nYas Air is an “involved person” within the meaning of the Iran (Sanctions) (Nuclear) (EU Exit) Regulations 2019. Yas Air is associated with the IRGC, who is or has been responsible for, engaged in, provided support for or facilitated a relevant nuclear activity, namely the development of a nuclear weapon delivery system in, or for use in, Iran.",
